#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<literal>Lieutenant Skat</literal> (from German <foreignphrase lang=\"de"
"\">Offiziersskat</foreignphrase>) is a fun and engaging card game for two "
"players, where the second player is either live opponent, or built in "
"artificial intelligence."
msgstr ""
"<literal>Poročnik Skat</literal> (iz nemščine <foreignphrase lang=\"de"
"\">Offiziersskat</foreignphrase>) je zabavna in privlačna igra s kartami za "
"dva igralca, kjer je drugi igralec bodisi živ nasprotnik bodisi vgrajena "
"umetna inteligenca."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The game is played using a single deck of cards. Cards are shuffled and "
"distributed amongst the players in such a way that half of them are face "
"down and half of them are open. Each participant plays one of the open cards "
"per turn. As soon as all the cards are played the round ends and points are "
"calculated and awarded."
msgstr ""
"Igra se igra z enim kompletom kart. Karte se premešajo in razdelijo med "
"igralce tako, da jih je polovica obrnjenih navzdol, polovica pa odprtih. "
"Vsak udeleženec igra eno od odprtih kart na potezo. Takoj, ko so odigrane "
"vse karte, se krog zaključi in točke se izračunajo in podelijo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to Play"
msgstr "Kako igrati"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid "Objective:"
msgstr "Cilj:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid "Score more than 60 points in a single game."
msgstr "Zberite več kot 60 točk v eni igri."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once dealing is finished each player ends up with 16 cards each. Cards are "
"displayed in two horizontal rows - four cards per row. Half of the cards are "
"face down and half are face up. As a player you can see the cards of your "
"opponent as well as your own. You can make a move then by clicking on any of "
"your cards which are currently face up. The opponent has to reply by "
"choosing a corresponding card form his/her own stack."
msgstr ""
"Ko je razdelitev končana, ima vsak igralec 16 kart. Karte so prikazane v "
"dveh vodoravnih vrstah - štiri karte na vrstico. Polovica kart je obrnjena "
"navzdol in polovica obrnjena navzgor. Kot igralec lahko vidite karte svojega "
"nasprotnika in svoje. Nato lahko naredite potezo s klikom na katero koli od "
"svojih kart, ki so trenutno obrnjene navzgor. Nasprotnik mora odgovoriti z "
"izbiro ustrezne karte iz svojega niza."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If your opponent is artificial intelligence, its cards will be chosen "
"automatically."
msgstr ""
"Če je vaš nasprotnik umetna inteligenca, bodo njegove karte izbrane "
"samodejno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once the exchange is finished values of the played cards are evaluated and "
"either you or your opponent is awarded points. The game is complete in 16 "
"rounds (when all of your and your opponent's cards have been played). After "
"the game ends your score is being compared to that of your opponent and the "
"player with the higher score wins the round."
msgstr ""
"Ko je menjava končana, se ovrednotijo vrednosti odigranih kart in vi ali vaš "
"nasprotnik dobite točke. Igra je zaključena v 16 rundah (ko so odigrane vse "
"vaše in nasprotnikove karte). Po koncu igre se vaš rezultat primerja z "
"rezultatom vašega nasprotnika in igralec z višjim rezultatom zmaga krog."

