#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Every player owns 16 cards. 8 of them are face down 8 of them are face up."
msgstr ""
"Vsak igralec ima v lasti 16 kart. 8 jih je obrnjenih navzdol, 8 jih je "
"obrnjenih navzgor."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A face down card can only be opened after a face up card covering it has "
"been played."
msgstr ""
"Karto, obrnjeno navzdol, je mogoče odpreti šele po odigrani karti, obrnjeni "
"navzgor, ki jo pokriva."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid "Each game has a randomly chosen <quote>trump</quote> card [8]."
msgstr "Vsaka igra ima naključno izbranega <quote>aduta</quote> karto [8]."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid "All four Jacks are counted as trumps and do not belong to their suits."
msgstr "Vsi štirje fanti se štejejo kot aduti in ne spadajo med njihove barve."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If a color (&eg; heart) is selected as <quote>trump</quote> all seven hearts "
"as well as all four Jacks count as trumps, making 11 trump cards."
msgstr ""
"Če je barva (&ie; srce) izbrana kot <quote>adut</quote>, se vseh sedem src "
"in vsi štirje fanti štejejo za adute, kar pomeni 11 adutov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Jacks beat each other in order (greatest to least): Cup->Spade->Heart-"
">Diamond."
msgstr ""
"Fanti se med seboj premagujejo v vrstnem redu (največji proti najmanj): križ-"
">pik->srce->kara."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The sequence of cards for a trump color: Jack of clubs, Jack of spades, Jack "
"of hearts, Jack of diamonds, Ace, Ten, King, Queen, Nine, Eight, Seven."
msgstr ""
"Zaporedje kart za adutovsko barvo: križev fant, pikov fant, srčev fant, "
"karov fant, as, desetka, kralj, dama, devetka, osmica, sedmica."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The sequence of cards for a non-trump color: Ace, Ten, King, Queen, Nine, "
"Eight, Seven."
msgstr ""
"Zaporedje kart za barvo brez aduta: as, desetka, kralj, dama, devetka, "
"osmica, sedmica."

