#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A special <quote>trump</quote> game is called the Grand. In this game no "
"suit is trump and only the four Jacks count as trump. This game type is "
"indicated by the symbol of a Jack's head [8] on the score board [6]."
msgstr ""
"Posebna igra <quote>adutov</quote> se imenuje Grand. V tej igri nobena barva "
"ni adut in samo štirje fanti štejejo kot adut. Ta vrsta igre je označena s "
"simbolom fantove glave [8] na semaforju [6]."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If player starts the round he has a choice of cards to play with, either a "
"card from a suite or a <quote>trump</quote> card."
msgstr ""
"Če igralec začne krog, lahko izbira med kartami, s katerimi lahko igra, "
"bodisi karto iz kompleta ali karto <quote>aduta</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Only the face up cards from the player's own stack can be used to play the "
"round."
msgstr ""
"Za igranje kroga se lahko uporabijo samo obrnjene karte iz igralčevega "
"kupčka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid "Player who wins the round starts the next one."
msgstr "Igralec, ki zmaga krog, začne naslednji krog."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The player who wins the round adds values of the cards played in that round "
"to his/her score."
msgstr ""
"Igralec, ki zmaga v krogu, svojemu rezultatu doda vrednosti kart, odigranih "
"v tem krogu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid "Player with more than 60 points wins the game."
msgstr "Igralec z več kot 60 točkami zmaga."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid "If both players finish with 60 points each the game ends in a draw."
msgstr "Če oba igralca končata s po 60 točkami, se igra konča z remijem."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:165
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For each game a certain amount of victory points is awarded and added to the "
"overall score."
msgstr ""
"Za vsako igro se dodeli določeno število zmagovalnih točk, ki se dodajo "
"skupnemu rezultatu."

