#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid "Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Strategije in nasveti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the game starts, the starting player should play any of the face up "
"cards from own stack. If the second player currently has face up cards that "
"are of the same suit as the card played, he has to reply with one of those "
"cards. If, however, the second player does not have a card of the same suit, "
"he can play with any other card including a <quote>trump</quote> card."
msgstr ""
"Ko se igra začne, mora začetni igralec odigrati katero koli od obrnjenih "
"kart iz svojega kupa. Če ima drugi igralec trenutno obrnjene karte, ki so "
"iste barve kot igrana karta, mora odgovoriti z eno od teh kart. Če pa drugi "
"igralec nima karte iste barve, lahko igra s katero koli drugo karto, "
"vključno z <quote>adutom</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If there is at least one <quote>trump</quote> card, the highest "
"<quote>trump</quote> wins both cards."
msgstr ""
"Če je vsaj en <quote>adut</quote> karta, premaga obe karti najvišji "
"<quote>adut</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If there is no <quote>trump</quote> card, the highest card of the suit "
"played by the starting player wins both cards."
msgstr ""
"Če ni <quote>aduta</quote>, premaga obe karti najvišja karta v barvi, ki jo "
"igra začetni igralec."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the replying player has no card of the requested suit and no "
"<quote>trump</quote> card, he has to play any card and the starting player "
"wins both cards."
msgstr ""
"Če igralec, ki odgovori, nima karte zahtevane barve in <quote>aduta</quote>, "
"mora odigrati katero koli karto in začetni igralec dobi obe karti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid "The player who wins the round leads the next one."
msgstr "Igralec, ki zmaga krog, vodi naslednjega."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently asked questions"
msgstr "Pogosto zastavljena vprašanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I play with a different deck of cards?"
msgstr "Ali lahko igram z drugim kompletom kart?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes. Refer to <link linkend=\"deck_change\">this</link> section of "
"'Interface Overview' for details."
msgstr ""
"Da. Za podrobnosti glejte <link linkend=\"deck_change\">ta</link> razdelek "
"»Pregled vmesnika«."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid "I have made a mistake. Can I undo?"
msgstr "Naredil sem napako. Ali lahko razveljavim?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. This game does not have an <quote>Undo</quote> feature."
msgstr "Ne. Ta igra nima funkcije <quote>Razveljavi</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I use the keyboard to play this game?"
msgstr "Ali lahko uporabljam tipkovnico za igranje te igre?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. This game cannot be played using keyboard."
msgstr "Ne. Te igre ni mogoče igrati s tipkovnico."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid "I cannot figure out what to do here! Are there hints?"
msgstr "Ne morem ugotoviti, kaj naj naredim tukaj! Ali obstajajo namigi?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. This game does not have a <quote>Hint</quote> feature."
msgstr "Ne. Ta igra nima funkcije <quote>Namig</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:219
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I have to quit the game now, but I am not finished yet. Can I save my "
"progress?"
msgstr ""
"Zdaj moram zapustiti igro, vendar še nisem končal. Ali lahko shranim svoj "
"napredek?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. This game does not have a <quote>Save State</quote> feature."
msgstr "Ne. Ta igra nima funkcije <quote>Shrani stanje</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:223
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I change players' names?"
msgstr "Ali lahko spremenim imena igralcev?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes. To change the names displayed on the right hand side of the game screen "
"refer to <link linkend=\"name_change\">this</link> section of 'Interface "
"Overview' for details."
msgstr ""
"Da. Če želite spremeniti imena, prikazana na desni strani zaslona igre, "
"glejte <link linkend=\"name_change\">ta</link> razdelek 'Pregled vmesnika' "
"za podrobnosti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid "Interface Overview"
msgstr "Pregled vmesnika"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Game Menu"
msgstr "Meni igre"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap><anchor id=\"new_game\"/"
">N</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap><anchor id=\"new_game\"/"
">N</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Nova</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starts a new game."
msgstr "Začne novo igro."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&End;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>End Game</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&End;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Končaj igro</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ends a running game."
msgstr "Konča tekočo igro."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Clear Statistics</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Počisti statistiko</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:268
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Clears the all time game memory.</action> This statistic is saved "
"when the game ended and shows the overall score and the amount of played and "
"won games per player. This is cleared with this menu item."
msgstr ""
"<action>Počisti pomnilnik vseh iger.</action> Ta statistika se shrani, ko se "
"igra konča in prikazuje skupni rezultat ter število odigranih in zmaganih "
"iger na igralca. To se počisti s to postavko menija."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zapusti</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quits the program."
msgstr "Zapusti program."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Settings Menu"
msgstr "Meni z nastavitvami"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:297
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Starting Player</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Zagon igralca</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selects whether player 1 (top) or player two (bottom) begins the next game."
msgstr ""
"Izbere, ali igralec 1 (zgoraj) ali igralec 2 (spodaj) začne naslednjo igro."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:307
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Player 1 Played By</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Igralec 1, ki ga igra</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:312
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Chooses who should play for player 1 (top). The player can be either "
"controlled by the local player with the mouse or the computer will control "
"it."
msgstr ""
"Izbere, kdo naj igra za igralca 1 (zgoraj). Igralca lahko upravlja lokalni "
"igralec z miško ali pa ga upravlja računalnik."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Player 2 Played By</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Igralec 2, ki ga igra</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Chooses who should play for player 2 (bottom). The player can be either "
"controlled by the local player with the mouse or the computer will control "
"it."
msgstr ""
"Izbere, kdo naj igra za igralca 2 (spodaj). Igralca lahko upravlja lokalni "
"igralec z miško ali pa ga upravlja računalnik."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:333
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Theme</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Tema</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:338
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Chooses a visual theme. This changes the appearance of the game but not of "
"the cards. Card decks are selected with their own menu item."
msgstr ""
"Izbere vizualno temo. To spremeni videz igre, ne pa tudi kart. Kompleti kart "
"so izbrani z lastnim elementom menija."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Select Card Deck…</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izberite komplet kart...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:348
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Choose the face and back of the card deck used for playing.</action> "
"You can select these in a preview dialog showing all card decks installed."
msgstr ""
"<action>Izberite sprednjo in zadnjo stran kompleta kart, ki se uporablja za "
"igranje.</action> To lahko izberete v pogovornem oknu za predogled, ki "
"prikazuje vse nameščene komplete kart."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:353
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some card decks or card sets are marked as scalable graphics (&SVG;) in the "
"dialog. Choosing them will display better quality of the graphics when the "
"game is scaled or enlarged. Fixed size graphics will loose quality when "
"resized different than their original size."
msgstr ""
"Nekateri kompleti kart ali kompleti kart so v pogovornem oknu označeni kot "
"razširljiva grafika (&SVG;). Če jih izberete, bo prikazana boljša kakovost "
"grafike, ko se igra pomanjša ali poveča. Grafika fiksne velikosti bo "
"izgubila kakovost, če bo velikost drugačna od prvotne velikosti."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:364
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Change Player Names…</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Spremeni imena igralcev…</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:369
#, no-c-format
msgid "Change the names of the players."
msgstr "Spremeni imena igralcev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally &i18n-lskat; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"and <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more information read the "
"sections about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings"
"\">Settings Menu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"Dodatno &i18n-lskat; ima skupno &kde; Elemente menija <guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu> in <guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu>, za več informacij preberite razdelke o "
"<ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">meniju z "
"nastavitvami</ulink> in <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-help"
"\">meni Pomoč</ulink> v &kde; Osnove."

